org.apache.flex.abc.visitors

Interface IVisitor

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    IABCVisitor, IClassVisitor, IMethodBodyVisitor, IMethodVisitor, IScriptVisitor, ITraitsVisitor, ITraitVisitor
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ABCDumpVisitor, ABCEmitter, ABCScopeBuilder, DeadCodeFilter, DelegatingABCVisitor, DelegatingClassVisitor, DelegatingMethodBodyVisitor, DelegatingMethodVisitor, DelegatingScriptVisitor, DelegatingTraitsVisitor, DelegatingTraitVisitor, NilABCVisitor, NilClassVisitor, NilMethodBodyVisitor, NilMethodVisitor, NilScriptVisitor, NilTraitsVisitor, NilTraitVisitor, PeepholeOptimizerMethodBodyVisitor, PoolingABCVisitor, PoolingABCVisitor.ClassVisitor, ScopedDefinitionTraitsVisitor

    public interface IVisitor
    Base interface for all visitors reachable from an IABCVisitor.

    Currently this interface exists so that clients can keep a collection of visitor's whose visitEnd() methods need to be called at some point in the future.

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void visitEnd()
      Indicates that no further method calls will be made on this visitor instance.

    • Method Detail

      • visitEnd

        void visitEnd()
        Indicates that no further method calls will be made on this visitor instance. Interfaces that derive from this interface add more specific meaning to this method.
